Regulations 2020.

title: Regulation 21(3) by substituting “to the public, for purchase at a fee not
heading: 2. The Forestry Regulations 2017 (S.I. No. 191 of 2017) are amended in
text_raw:
2. The Forestry Regulations 2017 (S.I. No. 191 of 2017) are amended in 
Regulation 21(3) by substituting “to the public, for purchase at a fee not 
exceeding the reasonable cost of doing so,” for “to the public”. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

7 October, 2020. 

CHARLIE MCCONALOGUE, 

Minister for Agriculture, Food and the Marine. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
“Iris Oifigiúil” of 9th October, 2020.
